acre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=7dafc646\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a>"},{"pid":"72c5ce3fbaae6d5a70bb94c12d540ee70c65bee7","tid":1608621,"uid":169040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"一名中五男生在荃灣疑中實彈槍 送院搶救<br />\n2019-10-01 HKT 19:11<br />\n<br />\n本港多區在國慶日發生嚴重衝突，荃灣大河道下午4時許，一名全副裝備的男子懷疑中實彈槍，左邊胸口流血，送院搶救。傷者的朋友證實，傷者是荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學一名中五男生。警方消息說，事發現場開過實彈槍。油麻地亦有警員懷疑曾開實彈槍示警，相信無射中人。<br />\n<br />\n灣仔、油麻地、黃大仙、深水埗、荃灣、沙田、屯門等地區，也爆發激烈警民衝突，警方在多區施放催淚彈驅散。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483685-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483685-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=d9b894f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483685-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d25af754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483685-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9f92ef59851614f4295824818212371912e3c11e","tid":1608621,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:12:50.000Z","msg":"瑪嘉烈醫院ICU<br />\n<br />\n左肺中彈<br />\n<br />\n曾志健（音）<br />\n<br />\n荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學學生，中五<br />\n<br />\n唔好讓手足被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊去跟進<br />\n另外一齊搵議員, 律師跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8883bad1c7513ae60a4fc3535183620fc746f01e","tid":1608621,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:02.000Z","msg":"荃灣青年疑中實彈重傷 證實為荃灣何傳耀中學中五學生<br />\n2019-10-01 HKT 18:20<br />\n荃灣大河道一名青年懷疑中實彈槍受重傷，他的朋友證實傷者是荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學一名中五男生，傷者的一班朋友到瑪嘉烈醫院了解情況，他們情緒激動，有人落淚。<br />\n<br />\n事發下午4時許，男傷者在荃灣大河道中槍後倒地，左邊心口流血，網上片段看到，傷者倒在地上後大叫「心口好痛」，要求送院。警方消息證實，事發現場開過實彈槍。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=8f960598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd0308a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"870b03d1bf4d0200ced928c74695928d723a8b14","tid":1608621,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"唔可以比831再發生<br />\n831 , 我地無證據, 無辦法<br />\n但而家有齊資料, 一定要100%跟進, 雖然我唔知可以點跟進"},{"pid":"045ad90870e098915fd823a9d7c214d90013fa1d","tid":1608621,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cfeec44992e9300a726e02178bc545babbb9904","tid":1608621,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人follow<br />\n<br />\n【17:30】中槍示威者姓曾，中槍後被送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，情況危殆，其友人趕赴醫院了解，表示傷者為中五學生，他自稱曾志健（音），送院時清醒，目前仍未能找到其家人。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人而家一齊去瑪嘉烈醫院? 唔想有義士被失蹤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人去"},{"pid":"af198a378f9a3ee373ac71448601f400dae0288f","tid":1608621,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"瑪嘉烈醫院ICU<br />\n<br />\n左肺中彈<br />\n<br />\n曾志健（音）<br />\n<br />\n荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學學生，中五"},{"pid":"338c94249f042cfd733320d9bc39e412825d4475","tid":1608621,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"我想出黎, 但無巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553ecd0b853ae6ec511b11a140207330488aefc4","tid":1608621,"uid":171866,"like":0,"di